  "text": "Nanocarriers can be submitted to an osmotic imbalance when injected in physiological media leading to morphological changes. In [CITATION_1] , polymersomes were osmotically stressed and characterized by combined TEM, DLS and SANS. Hypotonic shock leads to a swelling of the vesicles, and hypertonic shock leads to collapsed structures such as unilamellar vesicles transform into bilamellar vesicles, a transition that might strongly affect the drug transport and delivery.",
